REPLY QR RA AA
SECTION QUESTION
local. IN SOA
SECTION ANSWER
local. 3600 IN SOA nobody nobody 1 2 3 4 5
ENTRY_END

; positive subdomain
STEP 9 QUERY
ENTRY_BEGIN
SECTION QUESTION
serv.local. IN A
ENTRY_END
STEP 10 CHECK_ANSWER
ENTRY_BEGIN
